outputs.output_descr: Assists families and communities affected by the series of typhoons in 2006 in Bicol region, particularly Typhoon Reming, and aims to complement ongoing rehabilitation efforts and implement disaster risk reduction and management initiatives

project_descr: Comprehensive rehabilitation package for communities affected by Tropical Storm Durian in the Bicol Region in 2006
project_title: recovery for typhoon-affected communities in bicol
